               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) ዳዊት, Psalter (fols. <locus from="1r" to="152va"/>)I-<locus target="#1"/>) መዝሙረ፡ዳዊት“Psalms of  David” (fols. <locus from="1r" to="117v"/>) I-<locus target="#2"/>) መኃልየ፡ነቢያት “The Canticles of the Prophets” (fols. <locus from="118r" to="131r"/>) I-<locus target="#3"/>) መኃልየ፡መኃልይ፡ዘሰሎሞን“Song of Songs of Solomon” (fols. <locus from="131r" to="139r"/>) I-<locus target="#4"/>) ውዳሴ፡ማርያም“The Praise of Mary” (fols. <locus from="139ra" to="147va"/>) </p>
                     <p>I-<locus target="#5"/>) አንቀጸ፡ብርሃን“Gate of Light” (fols. <locus from="147va" to="152va"/>)</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
