                        <condition key="other">
                           <p>The sewing has been damaged and crudely repaired; quire III is loose. Fols. <locus target="#1"/>-<locus target="#2"/>
                              <locus from="126" to="152"/> are damaged by water, cockled. Scribbles are written in modern ink, on bottom margin of many folios.</p>
                           
