                        </layout>
                        <layout>
                           <p>One column: fols. <locus from="1r" to="139r"/> (the end of Text I-<locus target="#3"/>occupying half of fol. <locus target="#139r"/>is written in one column, even though the leaf is ruled for writing in two column)</p>
                           <p>Two columns: fols. <locus from="139r" to="152v"/>.</p>
                           
