                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">20th-century script;  careless, hasty hand. <note>
                           <p>Unknown. The name of the scribe has been erased from the concluding supplication, fol. <locus target="#152va"/>.</p>
                           
                        </note>
                        <note>
                           <p>- In order to accommodate longer text lines, the scribe employed compressed script on nearly each folio up to fol. <locus target="#19r"/>and runovers which are not marked or marked with thin black lines, fols. <locus target="#19v #20v #24v #41r #46r #47r #55r"/>etc.   </p>
                           <p>- The scribe reduced the size of the handwriting for Texts IV and V</p>
                        </note>
                        <seg type="rubrication">
                           Executed in the main hand
                           
                        </seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>

                     <decoNote type="other" xml:id="d2">
                        <p>Red threads are inserted in upper right corner of fols. <locus target="#1 #8 #43 #56 #72 #86 #101 #110 #118 #125 #131"/>.</p>
                        
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="mixed" xml:id="d3">
                        <p>Crude dichromic (black and red) ornamental bands are in the incipit page of Texts I-<locus target="#1"/>and I-<locus target="#4"/>(anthropomorphic motif: human face).</p>
                        
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <p>Fol. <locus target="#1"/>: ተግሣጽ፡ለኵሉ።</p>
                           <p>መዝሙር፡ዘዳዊት፡ሃሊ፡ሉያ።</p>
                           <p>ብፁዕ፡ብእሲ፡ዘኢሖረ፡በምክረ፡ረሲዓን፨</p>
                           <p>ወዘኢቆመ፡ውስተ፡ፍኖተ፡ኃጥአን፨…</p>
                           
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding contemporary="true">
                        <decoNote xml:id="b1">
                           <p>Ethiopian binding. Two wooden boards </p>
                           <p>(one third of the back board is broken off). </p>
                           <p>Two pairs of sewing stations. </p>
                           
                        </decoNote>
                     </binding>
                  </bindingDesc>
